languages.text: "Что-то непохоже, чтобы он был в благоговейном ужасе. Уверена, еще пара пустых угроз и расквашенных носов блюстителей, и вот тогда-то у него коленки затрясутся!"
"He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

languages.text: «A mí no me parece alguien que solo atienda al respeto y el temor, ¡pero unas cuantas amenazas sin fundamento y narices de agentes rotas más bastarán para que se arrodille!».
languages.original_text: "He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

languages.text: 「彼は畏怖と恐怖しか知らない人間には見えない。だが、もう少し空威張りして、エンフォーサーの鼻をへし折れば、膝を震わせてくれるに違いない！」
languages.original_text: "He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: “在我看来，这个人不像是‘只懂得敬畏与恐惧’的乌合之众。不过，当然，只要再说上几句空洞无物的威胁，再让几个执法者把自己鼻子搞断，那他肯定就会跪地求饶了！”
languages.original_text: "He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

languages.text: "Er sieht für mich nicht wie jemand aus, der nur Furcht und Entsetzen kennt. Aber ich bin sicher, nach einigen leeren Drohungen und ein paar eingeschlagenen Enforcer-Nasen wird er auf den Knien vor uns rutschen."
languages.original_text: "He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

languages.text: « Il ne m'a pas l'air de ne connaître que l'effroi et la terreur. Mais nul doute que quelques menaces en l'air accompagnées de nez de prévôts cassés le mettront à genoux ! »
languages.original_text: "He doesn't look to me like somebody who knows only awe and terror. But I'm sure a few more empty threats and busted enforcer noses will have him quivering on his knees!"

languages.text: "Bana yalnızca korku ve dehşetten anlayan biri gibi gelmedi. Fakat içi boş birkaç tehdit savrulması ve infazcı burunlarının kırılması karşısında dizlerinin bağının çözüldüğüne eminim!"
